

	 
      “Nepal’s Wealth Green Trees”  “Nepal’s Wealth Green Trees.” This is one of expressions many Nepali people use. The meaning of this expression is that Nepal is a very wealthy country in natural resources. There is millions of tress in the dense forests of Nepal. Yearly, millions and millions of money are made by producing wood and papers. Nepal is very famous for its natural scenery. It makes money from tourists who come to see Nepal’s natural scenery. Without trees, Nepal would not be as it is today. 
    
